node.text:
Hey family!! I’m so excited to help raise money for @nokidhungry . Me and Quest designed a spatula for the fundraiser🙌🏾 with @williamssonoma x @nokidhungry . Y’all know I had to tell Sheena it was for the kids because honey she got a Lil attitude with me!! 😂. 

Their goal is to raise $3.5 million this year – which is over 35 million meals for kids across the country who are not getting the food they need!
Also you can vote for my design! The designer whose spatula gets the most votes in their “Spatdown” Fan Favorite Competition will have an additional $5,000 donated to No Kid Hungry in their name by Williams Sonoma!  Help me raise money for the babies and get y’all a cute spatula at the same time🙏🏾. You can click link in my bio or order here: https://www.williams-sonoma.com/m/products/nkh-silicone-spat-2021-tabitha-brown/?cm_cat=Like2Buy&cm_ite=nkh21tabitha&cm_ven=socialmedia&cm_pla=product

Vote here: http://www.williams-sonoma.com/spatdown

Thank y’all for your love and support!! Let’s help end childhood hunger in America❤️🙏🏾 #tabithabtown #nokidhungry #endchildhoodhunger #agoodcause #donations

node.title: Sheena got a friend for a good cause! Click the link in my bio to order!

node.text: Honey @teamchancebasketball made some kinda pasta dish earlier today and had noodles leftover in the water, so I used them for a little evening Sunshine pasta!  Go easy on the pepper unless you want the sneezing 😂. Love y’all!! #tabithabrown #vegan #pasta #foodie

node.text: Spent some time at Venice beach today and was super blessed by these children!  I absolutely love to see children passionate about music and arts, it’s so inspiring!! Y’all keep on going @lacitywildcats ❤️. Love y’all!!! #tabithabrown #childrenareourfuture #venicebeach #musicheals #artisexpression

node.text:
My husband has been following @etthehiphoppreacher for years and has always wanted to meet him! Last night I celebrated his new journey by asking @etthehiphoppreacher to come and pour life into him and it was simply magical🙌🏿. @etthehiphoppreacher  thank you so much for blessing us, we love you!! @teamchancebasketball babe I believe in you so much and I am so excited for you🎉 i love you!  #timetotakeanewchance #tabithabrown #chancebrown #retirementparty 
 🎥 @coreyomar
Event planner @lenoiragency.la

node.title: Last night I surprised my husband with @etthehiphoppreacher 🙌🏿

node.text:
Happy National Crown day family!! Tonight is the first Crown Awards and I’m being honored 🙌🏾 and I’m so grateful!! 
@thecrownact is helping put an end to hair discrimination🙌🏾🙌🏾
Join me and some amazing Black women at 7PM ET on Facebook and YouTube as we celebrate Black hair independence and work together to #PassTheCROWN nationwide.
Sign the petition and learn more at thecrownact.com.  #endhairdiscrimination #tabithabrown #ourhairisourbusiness #spreadlove

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tabitha Brown on July 20, 2021 tagging @mo_storyteller. May be an image of 1 person, standing and footwear.

node.text:
Today I encourage you to be intentional about your happiness!! Focus on the positive and the light! You deserve it❤️. Love y’all!! 
📸 by @mo_storyteller 
#tabithabrown #inspire

node.text:
Hey family!! I’m so excited to help raise money for @nokidhungry . Me and Quest designed a spatula for the fundraiser🙌🏾 with @williamssonoma x @nokidhungry . Y’all know I had to tell Sheena it was for the kids because honey she got a Lil attitude with me!! 😂. 

Their goal is to raise $3.5 million this year – which is over 35 million meals for kids across the country who are not getting the food they need!
Also you can vote for my design! The designer whose spatula gets the most votes in their “Spatdown” Fan Favorite Competition will have an additional $5,000 donated to No Kid Hungry in their name by Williams Sonoma!  Help me raise money for the babies and get y’all a cute spatula at the same time🙏🏾. You can click link in my bio or order here: https://www.williams-sonoma.com/m/products/nkh-silicone-spat-2021-tabitha-brown/?cm_cat=Like2Buy&cm_ite=nkh21tabitha&cm_ven=socialmedia&cm_pla=product

Vote here: http://www.williams-sonoma.com/spatdown

Thank y’all for your love and support!! Let’s help end childhood hunger in America❤️🙏🏾 #tabithabtown #nokidhungry #endchildhoodhunger #agoodcause #donations
Sunshine☀️ Lasagna was on the dinner menu tonight😋🙌🏾. What did y’all have for dinner? #tabithabrown #vegan #foodie #lasagna
